race.comment: STANDLEE (2) has been narrowly beaten at this track his last three. Has raced a short-priced favourite in all and came back to this trip last time. Draws better today and Cormack sticks and is flying. Deserves another chance. CLEARLY GEORGE (3) is also busting to win. Led and finished just ahead of the above last time and he's going to give a big sight again. RESOLUTE LADY (9) was racing well before having tough runs from wide gates his two most recent in stronger grade. Draws inside today and has a handy 2kg claim. She can race forward and keep safe. MAGADAN (1) resumed here with a solid effort. Keeps a 3kg claim and maps well. He will be around the mark.
